 of rails and ruby</li><li>NoSQL (HBase, Hive, Redis, Hadoop) knowledge</li><li>Experience working on large-scale web applications</li><li>Ability to own projects end-to-end as demonstrated by significant open-source contributions, independent projects, team leadership, or startups</li><li>Detailed knowledge of performance and scalability, including front-end web browser performance analysis</li></ul><p>Resumes for engineering roles are reviewed directly by a senior member of our engineering team within 24 hours. If you&#39;re not sure which engineering role to apply for, just make your best guess. We&#39;d love to hear from you!</p>]]></description>
