ike the online ad market, search engines and SEM, e-commerce optimization, and user analytics.</li></ul><p>Resumes for engineering roles are reviewed directly by a senior member of our engineering team within 24 hours. If you&#39;re not sure which engineering role to apply for, just make your best guess. We&#39;d love to hear from you!</p>]]></description>
